edu.ucla.sspace.matrix

Interface FileTransformer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MatlabSparseFileTransformer

    public interface FileTransformer
    An interface for transforming matrix files of a particular format. Since each format has specific details regarding iteration, immplementations can efficiently do a transform simply by iterating through the file once and request the transformed value for each entry from an GlobalTransform instance.
    Author:
    Keith Stevens
